<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA612_04_IH_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_04.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_04_ih_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="5_green" class="is_star" lang="y">밑면이 정육각형인 각기둥 모양의 선물 상자입니다. 이 선물 상자의 모든 모서리의 길이의 합은 몇 ㎝인지 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_04_IH/0005_01.png" alt=""/>
            <p class="text1">4 ㎝</p>
            <p class="text2">4 ㎝</p>
          </div>
          <div class="input_wrap mt_20 gap_4">
            <math-field data-answer-single="72" text-align="center"></math-field>
            ㎝
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">
                  주어진 육각기둥의 모든 모서리의 길이는 4 ㎝이고, 모서리는 모두 18개입니다.<br />
                  ➔ (모든 모서리의 길이의 합)=4×18=72 (㎝)
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
